description: The eldest of all Sibylla. She is connected to ruling circles in Simulacrum, and was the only survivor of the destruction of Chor Dextra after that choir attempted to perform the Emerald Ri Maajon. She joins Chor Tempest at Guragief`s request, to try to sort out Rimone and the rest of the choir, and from there on she flies as a sagitta, paired with Rimone. She has mysterious political connections to a faction within the Simulacran administration. While initially rejected by her pair, she eventually forms a deep bond of affection with Rimone.
name: Dominuura
